<li>Writers who prefer to optimize content in Google Docs before publishing</li>
<li>Beginners who want the simplest possible traffic-light scoring system</li>
<li>Sites already running Yoast with no pain points (switching for the sake of switching adds risk)</li>
</ul>
<p>Yoast is the right choice when readability analysis, simplicity, and brand trust matter more than feature count.</p>
